#

Sous Vide Chicken Breast with Truffle Mashed Potatoes and Roasted Asparagus

$25
750 kcal
Difficulty: 80%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

GourmetDinner

Description

Succulent sous vide chicken breast paired with luxurious truffle-infused mashed potatoes and perfectly roasted asparagus.

Ingredients

  • Chicken Breast: 2 pieces
  • Salt: 1 tsp
  • Black Pepper: 1/2 tsp
  • Olive Oil: 2 tbsp
  • Fresh Thyme: 1 tsp
  • Butter: 3 tbsp
  • Russet Potatoes: 4 large
  • Truffle Oil: 1 tbsp
  • Heavy Cream: 1/2 cup
  • Parmesan Cheese: 1/4 cup
  • Asparagus: 1 lb
  • Garlic Powder: 1/2 tsp
